menu "Customise DVB Frontends"
	depends on DVB_CORE

comment "DVB-S (satellite) frontends"
	depends on DVB_CORE

config DVB_STV0299
	tristate "ST STV0299 based"
	depends on DVB_CORE
	help
	  A DVB-S tuner module. Say Y when you want to support this frontend.

